	(text_box "Layout guidelines for MAX8614x:\n- Connect all GNDs to a single ground plane and use one single via to PCB ground\n- Use different vias for all decoupling caps\n- PD_IN must be shielded by PD_GND\n- PD_GND on the layer where the MAX8614x is mounted, PG_IN under PD_GND\n- No traces over or under PD_GND. Isolate it with an additonal copper layer."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
